                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <article class="post ">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">ABONO PECUNIÁRIO DE FÉRIAS - PAGAMENTO</h3><h4>Saiba mais!</h4>
                            <ul class="info">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="text date">quarta-feira, 17 de agosto de 2016</div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="entyp-pencil-1"></i>
                                    <div class="text">Publicado por CONDUX</div>
                                </li>
                                
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/noticias/?cat=Legisla%E7%E3o+Trabalhista">
                                        <i class="entyp-list-1"></i>
                                        <div class="text">Legislação Trabalhista</div>
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                
                            </ul>
                            
                            <figure>
                                <img src="https://condux.com.br/site/imgnews/166c.jpg" alt="ABONO PECUNIÁRIO DE FÉRIAS - PAGAMENTO"/>
                                
                            </figure>
                            
                            <div class="content">
                            <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">: </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Abono Pecuni&aacute;rio de f&eacute;rias consiste em uma quantia em dinheiro que corresponde a &#8531; do per&iacute;odo de f&eacute;rias a que o empregado fizer jus. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">A convers&atilde;o de &#8531; das f&eacute;rias em abono pecuni&aacute;rio n&atilde;o deve ser contado com tempo de servi&ccedil;o e nem deve ser considerado nem antes nem depois das f&eacute;rias, tendo em vista que se trata de dinheiro.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O abono pecuni&aacute;rio significa converter em &#8531; da dura&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;rias em dinheiro, o valor do abono deve corresponder &agrave; metade do valor das f&eacute;rias.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Obs.: Os empregados que trabalham me regime de tempo parcial n&atilde;o poder&atilde;o converter &#8531; de suas f&eacute;rias em abono pecuni&aacute;rio.</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">I) F&eacute;rias Incompletas: </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O empregado que n&atilde;o fizer jus ao per&iacute;odo completo de f&eacute;rias por conta de faltas injustificadas, tamb&eacute;m poder&aacute; requerer o abono pecuni&aacute;rio, referente aos dias de f&eacute;rias que tiver direito. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Obs.: S&atilde;o consideradas faltas n&atilde;o justificadas aquelas que n&atilde;o foram remuneradas pelo empregador. </span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">II) F&eacute;rias Coletivas:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Nas f&eacute;rias coletivas, os pedidos individuas do abono pecuni&aacute;rio, nesse caso, deve ser objeto de acordo coletivo entre o empregador e o sindicato da categoria profissional, independendo de requerimento individual a concess&atilde;o do abono.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">III) Prazo para o Requerimento:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O &sect; 1&ordm; do art. 143 da CLT determina que o abono de f&eacute;rias dever&aacute; ser requerido at&eacute; 15 dias antes do t&eacute;rmino do per&iacute;odo aquisitivo. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O requerimento poder&aacute; ser feito por meio de carta endere&ccedil;ada &agrave; empresa em duas vias, ficando uma em poder do empregado devidamente protocolada, n&atilde;o podendo haver recusa no recebimento pelo empregador. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Para evitar que a solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o seja feita fora do prazo determinado, &eacute; aconselh&aacute;vel que a empresa fa&ccedil;a uma circular mensal, alertando aos empregados sobre o devido prazo. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">IV) Remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o, Pagamento em Dobro e Prazo de Pagamento:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O valor do abono pecuni&aacute;rio ser&aacute; calculado sobre a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;ria, j&aacute; acrescida do adicional de &#8531; do sal&aacute;rio normal. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">A legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o vigente determina que sempre que as f&eacute;rias forem concedidas ap&oacute;s o prazo concessivo, nos 12 meses subsequentes ao vencimento do respectivo per&iacute;odo, o empregador ter&aacute; de pagar em dobro a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o correspondente. A base de c&aacute;lculo do abono pecuni&aacute;rio acompanha a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;rias, sendo assim, sempre que as f&eacute;rias forem pagas em dobro, o abono tamb&eacute;m ter&aacute; de ser pago em dobro. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O art. 145 da CLT estabelece que o pagamento da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;rias e, se for o caso, o do abono, ser&aacute; efetuado at&eacute; dois dias antes do in&iacute;cio do respectivo per&iacute;odo. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">V) Recibo de Quita&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O valor do abono pecuni&aacute;rio ser&aacute; destacado no pr&oacute;prio recibo de quita&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;rias; a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o dos dias trabalhados no per&iacute;odo correspondente ao abono ser&aacute; paga normalmente como sal&aacute;rio na folha de pagamento do respectivo m&ecirc;s. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">VI) Incid&ecirc;ncia de INSS, FGTS e IR/Fonte:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">1. INSS</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> - N&atilde;o h&aacute; incid&ecirc;ncia de contribui&ccedil;&atilde;o previdenci&aacute;ria sobre o valor do abono pecuni&aacute;rio.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">2. FGTS</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> - N&atilde;o h&aacute; incid&ecirc;ncia de dep&oacute;sito para o Fundo de Garantia do Tempo de Servi&ccedil;o sobre o valor do abono pecuni&aacute;rio.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">3. IR/Fonte</span><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> - O valor do abono pecuni&aacute;rio, adicionado &agrave; remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o de f&eacute;rias, n&atilde;o servir&aacute; de base para c&aacute;lculo e reten&ccedil;&atilde;o do Imposto de Renda na Fonte, conforme o Ato Declarat&oacute;rio Interpretativo RFB n&ordm; 28/09.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">As f&eacute;rias devem sofrer tributa&ccedil;&atilde;o em separado dos sal&aacute;rios, isso significa dizer que no c&aacute;lculo do imposto incidente sobre as f&eacute;rias pagas num determinado m&ecirc;s n&atilde;o devem ser somados aos sal&aacute;rios pagos naquele mesmo m&ecirc;s. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">VII) Penalidades: </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">As infra&ccedil;&otilde;es ao disposto no cap&iacute;tulo de f&eacute;rias constante da CLT ser&atilde;o punidas com multa no valor de R$ 170,26 por empregado em situa&ccedil;&atilde;o irregular. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Caso haja reincid&ecirc;ncia, embara&ccedil;o ou resist&ecirc;ncia &agrave; fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o, com o objetivo de fraudar a lei, a multa ser&aacute; aplicada em dobro. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">VIII) Exemplos:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">1. Um empregado mensalista, com direito a 30 dias de f&eacute;rias relativas ao per&iacute;odo de 01/03/2007 a 29/02/2008, sendo que o mesmo optou por converter 10 dias das suas f&eacute;rias em abono pecuni&aacute;rio, qual ser&aacute; o valor das f&eacute;rias e do abono que o empregado tem direito?</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></p>
