</div>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">C&aacute;lculo: Remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o das f&eacute;rias</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">(20 dias x R$ 25,00) .&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. = R$ 500,00</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Adicional de &#8531; (R$ 500,00 x &#8531;) ................................. = R$ 166,67</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Abono pecuni&aacute;rio (10 dias x R$ 25,00) ...................... = R$ 250,00</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Adicional de &#8531; (R$ 250,00 x &#8531;) .&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. = R$ 83,33</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o bruta de f&eacute;rias - 8% x R$ 666,67 &hellip;.... = R$ 1.000,00</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">INSS sobre as f&eacute;rias - 8% x R$ 666,67 .&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. = R$ 53,33</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o l&iacute;quida de f&eacute;rias &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. = R$ 946,67</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">2. Pagamento dos dias trabalhados: </span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">No m&ecirc;s de mar&ccedil;o/08, o empregado fez jus &agrave; remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o bruta de R$ 275,00 (11 dias de saldo de sal&aacute;rio), correspondente ao per&iacute;odo trabalhado de 01/03/08 a 11/03/08.</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">O empregado recebeu a quantia total no m&ecirc;s de R$ 1275,00, compreendendo os 20 dias de f&eacute;rias com mais &#8531; (R$ 66,67), o abono pecuni&aacute;rio acrescido de &#8531; (R$ 333,33) e o sal&aacute;rio de 11 dias (R$ 275,00).</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><u><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Desconto do INSS</span></span></span></span></u></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">No dia 06/04/08 por ocasi&atilde;o do pagamento de saldo de sal&aacute;rio do m&ecirc;s de mar&ccedil;o/08, a empresa recalculou o desconto do INSS da seguinte forma:</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br />
</b></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">F&eacute;rias 20 dias com mais &#8531; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.&hellip;. = R$ 666,67</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Abono pecuni&aacute;rio (10 dias) com mais &#8531; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. &nbsp;= R$ 333,33</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Saldo sal&aacute;rio dos 11 dias &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..&hellip;&hellip; = R$ 275,00</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Total remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.... &nbsp;= R$ 1.275,00</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">C&aacute;lculo INSS (9% x R$ 666,67 f&eacute;rias + R$ 275,00 saldo e sal&aacute;rio) &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.... = R$83,13</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">INSS j&aacute; retido nas f&eacute;rias &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;...&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.... = R$ 53,33</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">INSS descontado no pagamento do saldo de sal&aacute;rio (R$ 83,13 - R$ 53,33) &hellip;.. = R$ 29,80</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Valor l&iacute;quido a receber (R$ 275,00 - R$ 29,80) &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. = R$ 245,20</span></span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Condux Consultoria</span></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
&nbsp;</p>
                            </div>
                            
                        </article>
                        
                        
